summary: Arthur D, Little, Ince, and Harvey Soce are two of the world's leading pharmacologists. They studied at Cornell University and the University of Massachusetts, Boston. Their work has been published in the journals Pharmacology, Biochemistry and Pharmacol. and Biophysics.
